This sample app shows how use Spring Social PayPal to login with a PayPal user and obtain identity information.

To run, simply import the project into your IDE and deploy to a Servlet 2.5 or > container such as Tomcat 6 or 7.
You can also deploy from the command line with:
$ mvn tomcat:run

Access the project at http://localhost:8080/spring-social-paypal-quickstart-30x/signin

This app was adapted from Spring Social Facebook Quickstart: https://github.com/SpringSource/spring-social-facebook